<section class="section getting-started-section">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Quickstart</p>
    <h1>Start coding with VexaScript in a few minutes</h1>
    <p class="lead">Install the published <code>vexascript</code> npm package, use the <code>vexa</code> CLI, add the VS Code extension, and embed Monaco-powered editors when you want interactive docs or demos.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid getting-started-grid">
    <article class="card getting-started-card">
      <div class="step-heading">
        <span class="step-badge">1</span>
        <h3>Install the CLI</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Use the published npm package and call the binary as <code>vexa</code>.</p>
{% highlightVexaScript %}
npm install -g vexascript
vexa --help
{% endhighlightVexaScript %}
    </article>
    <article class="card getting-started-card">
      <div class="step-heading">
        <span class="step-badge">2</span>
        <h3>Compile or run a file</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Create a <code>main.vx</code> file and use the CLI to execute or build it.</p>
{% highlightVexaScript %}
vexa run main.vx
vexa build main.vx -o dist/main.js
{% endhighlightVexaScript %}
    </article>
    <article class="card getting-started-card">
      <div class="step-heading">
        <span class="step-badge">3</span>
        <h3>Use the VS Code extension</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Install the published VS Code extension to get diagnostics, quick fixes, navigation, and language-aware editing while you work.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=soywiz.vexascript-vscodeext" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Install VS Code extension</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/syntax">Open syntax reference</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/cli">Open CLI guide</a>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="card getting-started-card">
      <div class="step-heading">
        <span class="step-badge">4</span>
        <h3>Embed Monaco in docs or apps</h3>
      </div>
      <p>The website bundle includes embeddable Monaco editors and a full workbench, so tutorials and product pages can run VexaScript directly in the browser.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button secondary" href="/embed">Open embed guide</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/playground">Try the playground</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
